metadata.name: Starchain #1
metadata.description: Starchain PFP is a collection of sci-fi NFT's on the Ethereum blockchain.  A temporal glitch in the ether conduit has spawned 11,111 fragmented android wizards. These remnants of the SuperAI, Prometheus, roam the wastelands of the West; scavenging digital artifacts to survive the wrath of the voidnet singularity.
